title: Snuff Box
description:
Edgy BBC-3 sketch comedy show starring and written by Matt Berry and Rich Fulcher (The Mighty Boosh). Both main characters take the actor's own names and play hangmen - Berry the 'High Executioner to the King of England' and Fulcher his assistant. Much of the action takes place in a gentlemen's club for hangmen, with sketches featuring various bizarre situations and characters throughout. 6 episodes x 232MB.

1. Rich's Mother
2. Matt's Diary  
3. Punchline
4. Oh Brothers
5. Love Triangle
6. Wedding
